medicineData.name: Ecosprin 75mg Strip Of 14 Tablets
medicineData.description: Ecosprin 75 tablet is an antiplatelet medicine. It is used to prevent the risk of heart attacks, stroke and angina. It is also used in patients who have had angioplasty. Blood clots can limit or block the passage of blood to essential organs, resulting in a heart attack or stroke.

medicineData.name: Dolo (Paracetamol) 650mg Strip Of 15 Tablets
medicineData.description: Dolo 650 tablet contains an active ingredient called paracetamol, which works by blocking the formation of certain chemicals that cause pain and fever in the body. This medicine can be used to treat various conditions such as headache, backache, migraine, toothache, body pain, and even fever associated with diseases like typhoid or the common cold.
